<component type="desktop">
    <id>io.github.kraflab.DSDA-Doom</id>
    <name>DSDA-Doom</name>
    <summary>Enhanced Doom source port</summary>
    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>GPL-2.0</project_license>
    <developer_name>Ryan Krafnick</developer_name>

    <url type="homepage">https://github.com/kraflab/dsda-doom</url>
    <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/kraflab/dsda-doom/issues</url>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.kraflab.DSDA-Doom.desktop</launchable>
    <description>
        <p>
            This is a successor of prboom+ with many new features, including:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Heretic, Hexen, MBF21, Doom-in-Hexen, UDMF, and MAPINFO support</li>
            <li>In-game console and scripting</li>
            <li>Full controller support</li>
            <li>Palette-based opengl renderer</li>
            <li>Debugging features for testing</li>
            <li>Strict mode for speedrunning</li>
            <li>Various quality of life improvements</li>
            <li>Advanced tools for TASing</li>
            <li>Rewind</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

